# Internal dev notes — kept locally, not on github.
#
# Repo policy: only `README.md` (in any directory) may be committed.
# All other markdown files are local-only dev notes / planning / handoff
# docs / skeptic reviews / audit reports / phase specs / timing reports.
#
# If you need to add a new docs file, it MUST be named README.md. Put it
# in its own subdirectory if you need multiple.
#
# This wildcard replaces the old piecemeal `AUDIT_*.md / PERF_*.md / ...`
# patterns — skeptic batches, planning docs, port notes, etc. kept leaking
# onto github because new filename prefixes weren't in the old list.
*.md
!README.md
!**/README.md
